{"tid":1241647,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有18歲以上選民入一入黎，搵咗啲資料話俾你聽究竟你果一票影響力幾大！","createTime":"2019-06-18T18:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T14:19:49.000Z","uid":21707,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"87f85f0d9dbcd249d42d9c1d97e3e649517bb008","tid":1241647,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T18:54:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">以下資料採至2015年區議會選舉官方網站</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我精選咗某幾個區既結果俾大家睇睇，其中彩池相差五票，如果我無睇漏應該係<span style=\"color: red;\">2015年</span>差距最少的一區 </span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4g18qu5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4g18qu5.png&h=9a6e4e78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rAsGLu5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrAsGLu5.png&h=1c01e0c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rgyrb96.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frgyrb96.png&h=5b2dbf41&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w16sF3r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw16sF3r.png&h=8bd72be2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">接落黎再睇睇<span style=\"color: red;\">2015年</span>區議會選舉既投票率</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2015年</span>選民登記人數超過<span style=\"color: red;\">三百萬</span><br />\n但實際投票人數只有<span style=\"color: red;\">一百四十六萬</span>，不到選民登記人數的一半，亦即實際投票率只有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">47.01%</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4bnC3iG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4bnC3iG.png&h=2a631db4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BDte5w1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBDte5w1.png&h=a07040d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再睇睇<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">18歲至30歲</span></span>及<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">60歲以上</span></span> 增幅</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">7.8% 約 5萬人</span></span><br />\n及 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">23.7% 約20萬人</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3W5894n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3W5894n.png&h=b7148d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦！<br />\n點解經過2014年雨革後，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2015年（47.01%）</span></span>既區選雖然較<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2011年（41.49%）</span></span>區選有5.52%增幅，但為何增幅最大的是60歲以上選民？<br />\n<br />\n60歲選民政治覺醒？<br />\n建制廢老票配動員力更強？<br />\n2015年雨革果班青年未夠18歲？<br />\n<br />\n2019年既六月，香港政治變天，建制同泛民既天平稱一下子扭轉過黎.<br />\n還有不到半年時間就到十一月區選<br />\n如果中間無咩政治大意外，泛民又應該如何保持氣勢？<br />\n仲未計今年區選新增<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">確認書DQ制度</span></span>，政府會試水溫DQ一兩個人還是大刀闊斧DQ一眾泛民？<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以一齊諗諗可以點做，亦希望泛民各黨勿再on99各自為政！只有唔夠半年時間，你地應該加緊做好區選協調工作，<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫助想空降or想挑戰自動當選區既後選人</span>，警告你地勿再以老大哥心態自居！<br />\n<br />\n而我地普通選民/網民又係咪投票前咩都做唔到呢？唔係！<br />\n我地可以了解下自己區有咩參選者，行過見到同佢地傾下計，得閒同屋企人或者隔離左右鄰居洗下腦或者做下義工幫幫佢地（參選者），唔鐘意幕前既咪試下網上做下文宣，大家齊心出少少力，好似呢個星期各位所負出既咁，我相信今年區選會有大改變的！<br />\n<br />\n香港人可以創造一次又一次奇蹟，100萬人上完街到200萬人上街，一齊再創造另一個投票奇蹟啦大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山，各自努力，共勉之。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講完！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌未講完.</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>未登記做選民既快啲去登記，你果一票好重要！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">200萬+1</span><br />\n果一位代表烈士亦代表著每一個人！</ins></span></span>"},{"pid":"44dda9b84f9705b56c8ab3ede1f1210c253f4d1f","tid":1241647,"uid":264717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T18:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a9940e37a7b455aea5fd13082449a4c8474113","tid":1241647,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T18:58:26.000Z","msg":"用手機排版眼都盲，訓教先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5997f27904195dbde68e9aa2e1d7ff20fa7e8225","tid":1241647,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:13:44.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900625d53bab040cb7fe8ff56e2c79d543e2b210","tid":1241647,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:18:34.000Z","msg":"差五票咁冤枉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ba6c691107a57789604500a244ec9f48bfd67e","tid":1241647,"uid":21707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:25:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MdPRqws.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMdPRqws.png&h=a3156384&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be726ae6489af920d1910848ebf57d120a509d17","tid":1241647,"uid":169207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:25:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">*******請廣傳*******<br />\n地點：立法會<br />\n620晚上 詩歌禱告馬拉松<br />\n621全日 美食節<br />\n<br />\n#雞蛋是必吃的<